text: Duncan Carmichael (8 November 1915 - 28 November 1984) was an English cricketer. He played nine first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club between 1936 and 1937. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1915 births Category:1984 deaths Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:People from Jalpaiguri
